{"id": "figure_001", "modality": "figures", "name": "Transformer Encoder-Decoder", "task": {"description": "Create a single 1920x1080 self-contained HTML file using ONLY inline CSS and inline SVG (no external files, no scripts, no images) that reproduces the canonical Transformer encoder-decoder architecture figure. Title 'Transformer (Encoder-Decoder)' at top in 32px bold. Two parallel vertical stacks side by side. LEFT 'Encoder' stack wrapped in a labelled 'Nx' container, bottom to top: 'Input Embedding', '+ Positional Encoding', 'Multi-Head Self-Attention', 'Add & Norm', 'Feed Forward', 'Add & Norm'. RIGHT 'Decoder' stack wrapped in a labelled 'Nx' container, bottom to top: 'Output Embedding (shifted right)', '+ Positional Encoding', 'Masked Multi-Head Self-Attention', 'Add & Norm', 'Encoder-Decoder Cross-Attention', 'Add & Norm', 'Feed Forward', 'Add & Norm'. Above the decoder: 'Linear', 'Softmax', 'Output Probabilities'. From the top of the encoder stack draw TWO labelled arrows 'Keys (K)' and 'Values (V)' routing rightward into the decoder's 'Encoder-Decoder Cross-Attention' box. Draw residual skip arcs on the OUTER side of each stack: one per 'Add & Norm' (2 on the encoder left, 3 on the decoder right). Each box is a labelled rounded rectangle; the two stacks share a baseline grid so corresponding rows align. The 'Nx' multiplier label appears once on each stack container. Use dimension annotation 'd_model = 512' near the embeddings. HARDEN (density + alignment): ALSO include (a) a LEGEND box that maps every distinct block color and every arrow/line style used in the figure, and (b) a small tensor-shape annotation on each major block (e.g. 'BxNxd'). Pack the figure densely with at least 14 labeled elements; every group of sibling blocks must be equal-size and share edges, with uniform gutters, and nothing may overlap or clip.", "requirements": ["All boxes (6 encoder sublayers, 8 decoder sublayers, Linear, Softmax, Output Probabilities, 2 Nx containers) are visible within the 1920x1080 viewport with no clipping at any edge", "No two boxes overlap each other", "Every box label text is fully contained inside its rectangle with no text overflowing the box edges", "Both 'Nx' multiplier labels are visible, one per stack container, and do not overlap any box", "The 'Keys (K)' and 'Values (V)' cross-attention arrows run from the encoder top into the decoder 'Encoder-Decoder Cross-Attention' box and neither passes through any other box", "The 'Keys (K)' and 'Values (V)' arrow labels do not overlap each other or any box", "Residual skip arcs (2 on encoder left, 3 on decoder right) do not pass through any box and do not overlap each other", "Encoder sublayer boxes have equal vertical gaps, and decoder sublayer boxes have equal vertical gaps (even spacing within each stack)", "The 'd_model = 512' annotation is legible and does not overlap any box or other text", "No element is within 10px of any viewport edge", "No horizontal or vertical scrollbar appears; all content fits inside 1920x1080", "A legend box maps every block color and arrow/line style used; each major block carries a tensor-shape annotation; sibling blocks are equal-size and edge-aligned with uniform gutters; no element overlaps or is clipped"]}, "runs": [{"run": 1, "ss_n_defects": 3, "ss_text_overlap": 1, "ss_clipped": 1, "ss_overflow": 0, "ss_total_tokens": 5969, "rv_n_defects": 0, "rv_text_overlap": 0, "rv_clipped": 0, "rv_overflow": 0, "rv_iterations": 1, "rv_total_tokens": 6228}, {"run": 2, "ss_n_defects": 0, "ss_text_overlap": 0, "ss_clipped": 0, "ss_overflow": 0, "ss_total_tokens": 6100, "rv_n_defects": 0, "rv_text_overlap": 0, "rv_clipped": 0, "rv_overflow": 0, "rv_iterations": 1, "rv_total_tokens": 6053}, {"run": 3, "ss_n_defects": 0, "ss_text_overlap": 0, "ss_clipped": 0, "ss_overflow": 0, "ss_total_tokens": 6202, "rv_n_defects": 0, "rv_text_overlap": 0, "rv_clipped": 0, "rv_overflow": 0, "rv_iterations": 1, "rv_total_tokens": 5308}], "ss_img": "images/figures/figure_001_ss.jpg", "rv_img": "images/figures/figure_001_rv.jpg", "ss_html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Transformer Architecture</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 20px;\n            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\n            background: #f8f9fa;\n            width: 1920px;\n            height: 1080px;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n        \n        .title {\n            font-size: 32px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            text-align: center;\n            color: #2c3e50;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n        \n        .legend {\n            position: absolute;\n            top: 80px;\n            right: 40px;\n            background: white;\n            border: 2px solid #34495e;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            padding: 15px;\n            font-size: 12px;\n            width: 200px;\n        }\n        \n        .legend-title {\n            font-weight: bold;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            color: #2c3e50;\n        }\n        \n        .legend-item {\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            margin-bottom: 5px;\n        }\n        \n        .legend-color {\n            width: 16px;\n            height: 16px;\n            margin-right: 8px;\n            border-radius: 3px;\n        }\n        \n        .legend-line {\n            width: 20px;\n            height: 2px;\n            margin-right: 8px;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"title\">Transformer (Encoder-Decoder)</div>\n    \n    <div class=\"legend\">\n        <div class=\"legend-title\">Legend</div>\n        <div class=\"legend-item\">\n            <div class=\"legend-color\" style=\"background: #3498db;\"></div>\n            <span>Embedding Layers</span>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"legend-item\">\n            <div class=\"legend-color\" style=\"background: #e74c3c;\"></div>\n            <span>Attention Layers</span>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"legend-item\">\n            <div class=\"legend-color\" style=\"background: #2ecc71;\"></div>\n            <span>Normalization</span>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"legend-item\">\n            <div class=\"legend-color\" style=\"background: #f39c12;\"></div>\n            <span>Feed Forward</span>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"legend-item\">\n            <div class=\"legend-color\" style=\"background: #9b59b6;\"></div>\n            <span>Output Layers</span>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"legend-item\">\n            <div class=\"legend-line\" style=\"background: #e74c3c;\"></div>\n            <span>K/V Connections</span>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"legend-item\">\n            <div class=\"legend-line\" style=\"background: #34495e; border-radius: 10px;\"></div>\n            <span>Residual Connections</span>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <svg width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" viewBox=\"0 0 1920 1080\">\n        <!-- Background -->\n        <rect width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" fill=\"#f8f9fa\"/>\n        \n        <!-- Encoder Stack Container -->\n        <rect x=\"150\" y=\"200\" width=\"350\" height=\"650\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-dasharray=\"10,5\" rx=\"10\"/>\n        <text x=\"325\" y=\"190\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"18\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#34495e\">Encoder (Nx)</text>\n        \n        <!-- Decoder Stack Container -->\n        <rect x=\"650\" y=\"200\" width=\"350\" height=\"750\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-dasharray=\"10,5\" rx=\"10\"/>\n        <text x=\"825\" y=\"190\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"18\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#34495e\">Decoder (Nx)</text>\n        \n        <!-- Encoder Stack -->\n        <!-- Input Embedding -->\n        <rect x=\"170\" y=\"750\" width=\"310\" height=\"60\" fill=\"#3498db\" stroke=\"#2980b9\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n        <text x=\"325\" y=\"775\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">Input Embedding</text>\n        <text x=\"325\" y=\"795\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"white\">BxNxd_model</text>\n        \n        <!-- Positional Encoding -->\n        <rect x=\"170\" y=\"680\" width=\"310\" height=\"50\" fill=\"#3498db\" stroke=\"#2980b9\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n        <text x=\"325\" y=\"705\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">+ Positional Encoding</text>\n        <text x=\"325\" y=\"720\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"white\">BxNxd_model</text>\n        \n        <!-- Multi-Head Self-Attention -->\n        <rect x=\"170\" y=\"600\" width=\"310\" height=\"60\" fill=\"#e74c3c\" stroke=\"#c0392b\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n        <text x=\"325\" y=\"625\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">Multi-Head Self-Attention</text>\n        <text x=\"325\" y=\"645\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"white\">BxNxd_model</text>\n        \n        <!-- Add & Norm 1 -->\n        <rect x=\"170\" y=\"530\" width=\"310\" height=\"50\" fill=\"#2ecc71\" stroke=\"#27ae60\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n        <text x=\"325\" y=\"555\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">Add & Norm</text>\n        <text x=\"325\" y=\"570\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"white\">BxNxd_model</text>\n        \n        <!-- Feed Forward -->\n        <rect x=\"170\" y=\"450\" width=\"310\" height=\"60\" fill=\"#f39c12\" stroke=\"#e67e22\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n        <text x=\"325\" y=\"475\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">Feed Forward</text>\n        <text x=\"325\" y=\"495\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"white\">BxNxd_ff</text>\n        \n        <!-- Add & Norm 2 -->\n        <rect x=\"170\" y=\"380\" width=\"310\" height=\"50\" fill=\"#2ecc71\" stroke=\"#27ae60\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n        <text x=\"325\" y=\"405\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">Add & Norm</text>\n        <text x=\"325\" y=\"420\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"white\">BxNxd_model</text>\n        \n        <!-- Decoder Stack -->\n        <!-- Output Embedding -->\n        <rect x=\"670\" y=\"850\" width=\"310\" height=\"60\" fill=\"#3498db\" stroke=\"#2980b9\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n        <text x=\"825\" y=\"875\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">Output Embedding (shifted right)</text>\n        <text x=\"825\" y=\"895\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"white\">BxNxd_model</text>\n        \n        <!-- Positional Encoding -->\n        <rect x=\"670\" y=\"780\" width=\"310\" height=\"50\" fill=\"#3498db\" stroke=\"#2980b9\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n        <text x=\"825\" y=\"805\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">+ Positional Encoding</text>\n        <text x=\"825\" y=\"820\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"white\">BxNxd_model</text>\n        \n        <!-- Masked Multi-Head Self-Attention -->\n        <rect x=\"670\" y=\"700\" width=\"310\" height=\"60\" fill=\"#e74c3c\" stroke=\"#c0392b\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n        <text x=\"825\" y=\"720\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">Masked Multi-Head</text>\n        <text x=\"825\" y=\"735\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">Self-Attention</text>\n        <text x=\"825\" y=\"750\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"white\">BxNxd_model</text>\n        \n        <!-- Add & Norm 1 -->\n        <rect x=\"670\" y=\"630\" width=\"310\" height=\"50\" fill=\"#2ecc71\" stroke=\"#27ae60\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n        <text x=\"825\" y=\"655\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">Add & Norm</text>\n        <text x=\"825\" y=\"670\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"white\">BxNxd_model</text>\n        \n        <!-- Encoder-Decoder Cross-Attention -->\n        <rect x=\"670\" y=\"550\" width=\"310\" height=\"60\" fill=\"#e74c3c\" stroke=\"#c0392b\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n        <text x=\"825\" y=\"575\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">Encoder-Decoder</text>\n        <text x=\"825\" y=\"590\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">Cross-Attention</text>\n        <text x=\"825\" y=\"605\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"white\">BxNxd_model</text>\n        \n        <!-- Add & Norm 2 -->\n        <rect x=\"670\" y=\"480\" width=\"310\" height=\"50\" fill=\"#2ecc71\" stroke=\"#27ae60\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n        <text x=\"825\" y=\"505\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">Add & Norm</text>\n        <text x=\"825\" y=\"520\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"white\">BxNxd_model</text>\n        \n        <!-- Feed Forward -->\n        <rect x=\"670\" y=\"400\" width=\"310\" height=\"60\" fill=\"#f39c12\" stroke=\"#e67e22\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n        <text x=\"825\" y=\"425\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">Feed Forward</text>\n        <text x=\"825\" y=\"445\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"white\">BxNxd_ff</text>\n        \n        <!-- Add & Norm 3 -->\n        <rect x=\"670\" y=\"330\" width=\"310\" height=\"50\" fill=\"#2ecc71\" stroke=\"#27ae60\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n        <text x=\"825\" y=\"355\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">Add & Norm</text>\n        <text x=\"825\" y=\"370\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"white\">BxNxd_model</text>\n        \n        <!-- Output Layers -->\n        <!-- Linear -->\n        <rect x=\"670\" y=\"260\" width=\"310\" height=\"50\" fill=\"#9b59b6\" stroke=\"#8e44ad\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n        <text x=\"825\" y=\"285\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">Linear</text>\n        <text x=\"825\" y=\"300\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"white\">BxNxV</text>\n        \n        <!-- Softmax -->\n        <rect x=\"670\" y=\"210\" width=\"310\" height=\"40\" fill=\"#9b59b6\" stroke=\"#8e44ad\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n        <text x=\"825\" y=\"235\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">Softmax</text>\n        \n        <!-- Output Probabilities -->\n        <rect x=\"670\" y=\"160\" width=\"310\" height=\"40\" fill=\"#9b59b6\" stroke=\"#8e44ad\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n        <text x=\"825\" y=\"185\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">Output Probabilities</text>\n        \n        <!-- K/V Arrows from Encoder to Decoder -->\n        <!-- Keys Arrow -->\n        <path d=\"M 480 405 Q 550 405 550 580 Q 550 580 670 580\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#e74c3c\" stroke-width=\"3\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        <text x=\"560\" y=\"400\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#e74c3c\">Keys (K)</text>\n        \n        <!-- Values Arrow -->\n        <path d=\"M 480 420 Q 570 420 570 590 Q 570 590 670 590\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#e74c3c\" stroke-width=\"3\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        <text x=\"580\" y=\"415\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#e74c3c\">Values (V)</text>\n        \n        <!-- Residual Connections - Encoder -->\n        <!-- Residual 1 -->\n        <path d=\"M 140 630 Q 120 630 120 555 Q 120 555 140 555\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/>\n        \n        <!-- Residual 2 -->\n        <path d=\"M 140 480 Q 100 480 100 405 Q 100 405 140 405\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/>\n        \n        <!-- Residual Connections - Decoder -->\n        <!-- Residual 1 -->\n        <path d=\"M 1020 730 Q 1040 730 1040 655 Q 1040 655 1020 655\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/>\n        \n        <!-- Residual 2 -->\n        <path d=\"M 1020 580 Q 1060 580 1060 505 Q 1060 505 1020 505\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/>\n        \n        <!-- Residual 3 -->\n        <path d=\"M 1020 430 Q 1080 430 1080 355 Q 1080 355 1020 355\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"3\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/>\n        \n        <!-- Dimension Annotation -->\n        <text x=\"50\" y=\"780\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#34495e\">d_model = 512</text>\n        \n        <!-- Arrow marker definition -->\n        <defs>\n            <marker id=\"arrowhead\" markerWidth=\"10\" markerHeight=\"7\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"3.5\" orient=\"auto\">\n                <polygon points=\"0 0, 10 3.5, 0 7\" fill=\"#e74c3c\"/>\n            </marker>\n        </defs>\n        \n        <!-- Flow arrows within stacks -->\n        <!-- Encoder flow -->\n        <path d=\"M 325 750 L 325 730\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#flow-arrow)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 325 680 L 325 660\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#flow-arrow)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 325 600 L 325 580\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#flow-arrow)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 325 530 L 325 510\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#flow-arrow)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 325 450 L 325 430\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#flow-arrow)\"/>\n        \n        <!-- Decoder flow -->\n        <path d=\"M 825 850 L 825 830\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#flow-arrow)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 825 780 L 825 760\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#flow-arrow)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 825 700 L 825 680\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#flow-arrow)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 825 630 L 825 610\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#flow-arrow)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 825 550 L 825 530\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#flow-arrow)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 825 480 L 825 460\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#flow-arrow)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 825 400 L 825 380\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#flow-arrow)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 825 330 L 825 310\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#flow-arrow)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 825 260 L 825 250\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#flow-arrow)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 825 210 L 825 200\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"2\" marker-end=\"url(#flow-arrow)\"/>\n        \n        <!-- Flow arrow marker -->\n        <defs>\n            <marker id=\"flow-arrow\" markerWidth=\"8\" markerHeight=\"6\" refX=\"7\" refY=\"3\" orient=\"auto\">\n                <polygon points=\"0 0, 8 3, 0 6\" fill=\"#34495e\"/>\n            </marker>\n        </defs>\n    </svg>\n</body>\n</html>", "rv_html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Transformer Architecture</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 20px;\n            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\n            background: #f8f9fa;\n            width: 1920px;\n            height: 1080px;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n        \n        .title {\n            font-size: 32px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            text-align: center;\n            color: #2c3e50;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n        \n        .dimension-note {\n            font-size: 14px;\n            color: #7f8c8d;\n            font-style: italic;\n        }\n        \n        .legend {\n            position: absolute;\n            right: 20px;\n            top: 80px;\n            background: white;\n            border: 2px solid #34495e;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            padding: 15px;\n            font-size: 12px;\n            width: 200px;\n        }\n        \n        .legend-title {\n            font-weight: bold;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            color: #2c3e50;\n        }\n        \n        .legend-item {\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            margin-bottom: 5px;\n        }\n        \n        .legend-color {\n            width: 16px;\n            height: 16px;\n            margin-right: 8px;\n            border-radius: 3px;\n        }\n        \n        .legend-line {\n            width: 20px;\n            height: 2px;\n            margin-right: 8px;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"title\">Transformer (Encoder-Decoder)</div>\n    \n    <div class=\"legend\">\n        <div class=\"legend-title\">Legend</div>\n        <div class=\"legend-item\">\n            <div class=\"legend-color\" style=\"background: #3498db;\"></div>\n            <span>Embedding Layers</span>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"legend-item\">\n            <div class=\"legend-color\" style=\"background: #e74c3c;\"></div>\n            <span>Attention Layers</span>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"legend-item\">\n            <div class=\"legend-color\" style=\"background: #f39c12;\"></div>\n            <span>Normalization</span>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"legend-item\">\n            <div class=\"legend-color\" style=\"background: #27ae60;\"></div>\n            <span>Feed Forward</span>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"legend-item\">\n            <div class=\"legend-color\" style=\"background: #9b59b6;\"></div>\n            <span>Output Layers</span>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"legend-item\">\n            <div class=\"legend-line\" style=\"background: #2c3e50;\"></div>\n            <span>Data Flow</span>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"legend-item\">\n            <div class=\"legend-line\" style=\"background: #e67e22; height: 3px;\"></div>\n            <span>Cross-Attention</span>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"legend-item\">\n            <div style=\"width: 20px; height: 12px; border: 2px solid #34495e; border-radius: 6px; margin-right: 8px; background: none;\"></div>\n            <span>Residual Skip</span>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    \n    <svg width=\"1680\" height=\"900\" viewBox=\"0 0 1680 900\" style=\"margin-left: 20px;\">\n        <!-- Encoder Stack Container -->\n        <rect x=\"50\" y=\"100\" width=\"300\" height=\"650\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-dasharray=\"5,5\" rx=\"10\"/>\n        <text x=\"60\" y=\"90\" font-size=\"16\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#34495e\">Encoder (Nx)</text>\n        \n        <!-- Decoder Stack Container -->\n        <rect x=\"450\" y=\"100\" width=\"300\" height=\"750\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-dasharray=\"5,5\" rx=\"10\"/>\n        <text x=\"460\" y=\"90\" font-size=\"16\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#34495e\">Decoder (Nx)</text>\n        \n        <!-- Encoder Stack -->\n        <!-- Input Embedding -->\n        <rect x=\"70\" y=\"650\" width=\"260\" height=\"60\" fill=\"#3498db\" stroke=\"#2980b9\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n        <text x=\"200\" y=\"675\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">Input Embedding</text>\n        <text x=\"200\" y=\"695\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\">B\u00d7N\u00d7d_model</text>\n        \n        <!-- Positional Encoding -->\n        <rect x=\"70\" y=\"580\" width=\"260\" height=\"50\" fill=\"#3498db\" stroke=\"#2980b9\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n        <text x=\"200\" y=\"600\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">+ Positional Encoding</text>\n        <text x=\"200\" y=\"615\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\">B\u00d7N\u00d7d_model</text>\n        \n        <!-- Multi-Head Self-Attention -->\n        <rect x=\"70\" y=\"500\" width=\"260\" height=\"60\" fill=\"#e74c3c\" stroke=\"#c0392b\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n        <text x=\"200\" y=\"525\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">Multi-Head Self-Attention</text>\n        <text x=\"200\" y=\"545\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\">B\u00d7N\u00d7d_model</text>\n        \n        <!-- Add & Norm 1 -->\n        <rect x=\"70\" y=\"430\" width=\"260\" height=\"50\" fill=\"#f39c12\" stroke=\"#e67e22\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n        <text x=\"200\" y=\"450\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">Add & Norm</text>\n        <text x=\"200\" y=\"465\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\">B\u00d7N\u00d7d_model</text>\n        \n        <!-- Feed Forward -->\n        <rect x=\"70\" y=\"350\" width=\"260\" height=\"60\" fill=\"#27ae60\" stroke=\"#229954\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n        <text x=\"200\" y=\"375\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">Feed Forward</text>\n        <text x=\"200\" y=\"395\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\">B\u00d7N\u00d7d_ff\u2192d_model</text>\n        \n        <!-- Add & Norm 2 -->\n        <rect x=\"70\" y=\"280\" width=\"260\" height=\"50\" fill=\"#f39c12\" stroke=\"#e67e22\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n        <text x=\"200\" y=\"300\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">Add & Norm</text>\n        <text x=\"200\" y=\"315\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\">B\u00d7N\u00d7d_model</text>\n        \n        <!-- Decoder Stack -->\n        <!-- Output Embedding -->\n        <rect x=\"470\" y=\"750\" width=\"260\" height=\"60\" fill=\"#3498db\" stroke=\"#2980b9\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n        <text x=\"600\" y=\"770\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">Output Embedding</text>\n        <text x=\"600\" y=\"785\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\">(shifted right)</text>\n        <text x=\"600\" y=\"800\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\">B\u00d7M\u00d7d_model</text>\n        \n        <!-- Positional Encoding -->\n        <rect x=\"470\" y=\"680\" width=\"260\" height=\"50\" fill=\"#3498db\" stroke=\"#2980b9\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n        <text x=\"600\" y=\"700\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">+ Positional Encoding</text>\n        <text x=\"600\" y=\"715\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\">B\u00d7M\u00d7d_model</text>\n        \n        <!-- Masked Multi-Head Self-Attention -->\n        <rect x=\"470\" y=\"600\" width=\"260\" height=\"60\" fill=\"#e74c3c\" stroke=\"#c0392b\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n        <text x=\"600\" y=\"620\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">Masked Multi-Head</text>\n        <text x=\"600\" y=\"635\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">Self-Attention</text>\n        <text x=\"600\" y=\"650\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\">B\u00d7M\u00d7d_model</text>\n        \n        <!-- Add & Norm 1 -->\n        <rect x=\"470\" y=\"530\" width=\"260\" height=\"50\" fill=\"#f39c12\" stroke=\"#e67e22\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n        <text x=\"600\" y=\"550\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">Add & Norm</text>\n        <text x=\"600\" y=\"565\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\">B\u00d7M\u00d7d_model</text>\n        \n        <!-- Encoder-Decoder Cross-Attention -->\n        <rect x=\"470\" y=\"450\" width=\"260\" height=\"60\" fill=\"#e74c3c\" stroke=\"#c0392b\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n        <text x=\"600\" y=\"470\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">Encoder-Decoder</text>\n        <text x=\"600\" y=\"485\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">Cross-Attention</text>\n        <text x=\"600\" y=\"500\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\">B\u00d7M\u00d7d_model</text>\n        \n        <!-- Add & Norm 2 -->\n        <rect x=\"470\" y=\"380\" width=\"260\" height=\"50\" fill=\"#f39c12\" stroke=\"#e67e22\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n        <text x=\"600\" y=\"400\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">Add & Norm</text>\n        <text x=\"600\" y=\"415\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\">B\u00d7M\u00d7d_model</text>\n        \n        <!-- Feed Forward -->\n        <rect x=\"470\" y=\"300\" width=\"260\" height=\"60\" fill=\"#27ae60\" stroke=\"#229954\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n        <text x=\"600\" y=\"325\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">Feed Forward</text>\n        <text x=\"600\" y=\"345\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\">B\u00d7M\u00d7d_ff\u2192d_model</text>\n        \n        <!-- Add & Norm 3 -->\n        <rect x=\"470\" y=\"230\" width=\"260\" height=\"50\" fill=\"#f39c12\" stroke=\"#e67e22\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n        <text x=\"600\" y=\"250\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">Add & Norm</text>\n        <text x=\"600\" y=\"265\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\">B\u00d7M\u00d7d_model</text>\n        \n        <!-- Output Layers -->\n        <!-- Linear -->\n        <rect x=\"470\" y=\"160\" width=\"260\" height=\"50\" fill=\"#9b59b6\" stroke=\"#8e44ad\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n        <text x=\"600\" y=\"180\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">Linear</text>\n        <text x=\"600\" y=\"195\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\">B\u00d7M\u00d7vocab_size</text>\n        \n        <!-- Softmax -->\n        <rect x=\"470\" y=\"100\" width=\"260\" height=\"50\" fill=\"#9b59b6\" stroke=\"#8e44ad\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n        <text x=\"600\" y=\"120\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">Softmax</text>\n        <text x=\"600\" y=\"135\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\">B\u00d7M\u00d7vocab_size</text>\n        \n        <!-- Output Probabilities -->\n        <rect x=\"470\" y=\"30\" width=\"260\" height=\"50\" fill=\"#9b59b6\" stroke=\"#8e44ad\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n        <text x=\"600\" y=\"50\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">Output Probabilities</text>\n        <text x=\"600\" y=\"65\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\">B\u00d7M\u00d7vocab_size</text>\n        \n        <!-- Data Flow Arrows -->\n        <!-- Encoder vertical flow -->\n        <path d=\"M 200 650 L 200 630\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 200 580 L 200 560\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 200 500 L 200 480\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 200 430 L 200 410\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 200 350 L 200 330\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        \n        <!-- Decoder vertical flow -->\n        <path d=\"M 600 750 L 600 730\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 600 680 L 600 660\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 600 600 L 600 580\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 600 530 L 600 510\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 600 450 L 600 430\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 600 380 L 600 360\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 600 300 L 600 280\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 600 230 L 600 210\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 600 160 L 600 150\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        <path d=\"M 600 100 L 600 80\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n        \n        <!-- Cross-attention arrows from encoder -->\n        <!-- Keys arrow -->\n        <path d=\"M 330 305 Q 390 305 390 480 L 470 480\" stroke=\"#e67e22\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-orange)\"/>\n        <text x=\"380\" y=\"300\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#e67e22\">Keys (K)</text>\n        \n        <!-- Values arrow -->\n        <path d=\"M 330 285 Q 410 285 410 470 L 470 470\" stroke=\"#e67e22\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-orange)\"/>\n        <text x=\"400\" y=\"280\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#e67e22\">Values (V)</text>\n        \n        <!-- Residual Skip Connections -->\n        <!-- Encoder skip 1 -->\n        <path d=\"M 40 530 Q 30 530 30 455 Q 30 430 40 430\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke-dasharray=\"3,3\"/>\n        \n        <!-- Encoder skip 2 -->\n        <path d=\"M 40 380 Q 20 380 20 305 Q 20 280 40 280\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke-dasharray=\"3,3\"/>\n        \n        <!-- Decoder skip 1 -->\n        <path d=\"M 760 630 Q 770 630 770 555 Q 770 530 760 530\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke-dasharray=\"3,3\"/>\n        \n        <!-- Decoder skip 2 -->\n        <path d=\"M 760 480 Q 780 480 780 405 Q 780 380 760 380\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke-dasharray=\"3,3\"/>\n        \n        <!-- Decoder skip 3 -->\n        <path d=\"M 760 330 Q 790 330 790 255 Q 790 230 760 230\" stroke=\"#34495e\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke-dasharray=\"3,3\"/>\n        \n        <!-- Dimension annotation -->\n        <text x=\"200\" y=\"740\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"#7f8c8d\" font-style=\"italic\">d_model = 512</text>\n        \n        <!-- Arrow markers -->\n        <defs>\n            <marker id=\"arrowhead\" markerWidth=\"10\" markerHeight=\"7\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"3.5\" orient=\"auto\">\n                <polygon points=\"0 0, 10 3.5, 0 7\" fill=\"#2c3e50\"/>\n            </marker>\n            <marker id=\"arrowhead-orange\" markerWidth=\"10\" markerHeight=\"7\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"3.5\" orient=\"auto\">\n                <polygon points=\"0 0, 10 3.5, 0 7\" fill=\"#e67e22\"/>\n            </marker>\n        </defs>\n    </svg>\n</body>\n</html>"}